column2: SELECT ALL   p.objID,   p.RA,    p.DEC,    p.petromag_u_err,    p.petromag_u,   p.petromag_g,   p.petromag_g_err,   p.petromag_r,   p.petromag_r_err,   s.z,   s.z_err,   GIDX.lick_mgb,   GIDX.lick_mgb_err,     GIDX.lick_mg2,   GIDX.lick_mg2_err,   GIDX.lick_fe5#,     GIDX.lick_fe5#_err,   GIDX.lick_fe4#,     GIDX.lick_fe4#_err,   GIDX.lick_fe5#,     GIDX.lick_fe5#_err,   GIDX.lick_fe5#,   GIDX.lick_fe5#_err,   GIDX.lick_hda,   GIDX.lick_hda_err,   GIDX.lick_hga,   GIDX.lick_hga_err,        GLN.hei_#_reqw,   GLN.hei_#_reqw_err,   GLN.h_alpha_reqw,   GLN.h_alpha_reqw_err,   GLN.h_beta_reqw,   GLN.h_beta_reqw_err,     GLN.h_alpha_flux,   GLN.h_alpha_flux_err,   GLN.h_beta_flux,   GLN.h_beta_flux_err          into mydb.lick_sdsssample from PhotoObj AS p      JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid      JOIN galSpecIndx AS GIDX ON s.specobjid = GIDX.specobjid      JOIN galSpecLine AS GLN ON s.specobjid = GLN.specobjid        WHERE     p.petroMag_r <#    AND p.petroMag_g <#   AND p.petroMag_u <#   AND s.class=&&&    AND s.z>#   AND s.z<#
